telemetry.event.performance_metrics.desc:
Tlamatilistli īka Minecraft-chīwāltilisihitlakolistli tēchpalēwia mā tikīxkwalchīwakan māwiltilistli inik miak tētlamachilissoh sistemah.
Māwiltilisyankwililistli mopīwia inik tēchpalēwīs tikīxnamiktīsseh tlachīwāltilisihitlakolistli inik yankwīk Minecraft-yankwililistli.
telemetry.event.world_load_times.descrip: Moneki tikkwāmachilīsseh kēn weli wahkāwa inik tionkalakis sē tlāltikpaktli, īwān kēn inōn mopatla teipan. Mā tikittakan sē tlamachiyōmakalistli, ihkwāk tikīnpīwiah yankwīk tlamantinih noso tikīnchīwah wēyi tlapatlalistinih, moneki tikittasseh kēn inōn kipahyōtīs tlanēxtiliskāwitl.
telemetry.event.world_load_times.title: Tlāltikpaksēnkāwaliskāwitl
telemetry.event.world_loaded.description:
Tlān tikmatih kēn māwiltiānih māwiltiah Minecraft (kēnwak tlen iwkāyōtl, tlatekiwihkētl tlayankwīkachihchīwalli noso kalmelaktli, īwān māwiltilisyankwililistli) tēchmākāwa mā tikīxkwalchīwakan tlen māwiltiānih achiyok kinekih.
Nē "tlasēnkāwalli tlāltikpaktli" ēltok sēntik "tlatemōwilli tlāltikpaktli" īka tikmatisseh kēniwkāpān wahkāwki māwiltiliskwentah.
telemetry.event.world_loaded.title: Tlasēnkāwalli tlāltikpaktli
telemetry.event.world_unloaded.descripti:
This event is paired with the World Loaded event to calculate how long the world session has lasted.
The duration (in seconds and ticks) is measured when a world session has ended (quitting to title, disconnecting from a server).
